    <h1>Guidelines</h1>
    <div align="justify" style="border-bottom:1px dotted #D3D4D5; padding-bottom:10px;">
 <div id="center">
            <p id="teststext"><h2>Do's </h2></p>
            <p id="plaintext">1. Be in time for   class </p>
            <p id="plaintext">2. Keep your   surroundings (room, walls, corridors etc.) clean </p>
            <p id="plaintext">3. Appear in all the   internal examinations </p>
            <p id="plaintext">4. Handle all the   campus resources carefully </p>
            <p id="plaintext">5. Be attentive to   and appreciative of the visitors </p>
            <p id="plaintext">6. Participate in the   lectures / presentation given by the faculty (external as well as internal) </p>
            <p id="plaintext">7. Dress decently </p>
            <p id="plaintext">8. Switch the fans   &amp; lights off when classroom is not in use </p>
            <p id="plaintext">9. Approach faculty /   Mentor for Counseling </p>
            <p id="plaintext">10. Inform the   concerned authority about mishaps and accidents </p>
            <br />
            <br />
            <p id="teststext"><h2>Dont's</h2> </p>
            <p id="plaintext">1. Being absent on   the reopening day after the vacation (Summer &amp; Winter) </p>
            <p id="plaintext">2. Being late for the   class after breaks (Lunch &amp; Tea) </p>
            <p id="plaintext">3. Having a   non-serious attitude towards studies and campus in general </p>
            <p id="plaintext">4. Having lack of   commitment to the institution </p>
            <p id="plaintext">5. Being absent   without prior intimation </p>
            <p id="plaintext">6. Being absent   during the internal examinations / tests </p>
            <p id="plaintext">7. Being absent a day   before internals / Presentations etc </p>
            <p id="plaintext">8. Littering the   class rooms &amp; corridors </p>
            <p id="plaintext">9. Talking during   guest lecture </p>
            <p id="plaintext">10. Talking in the   classroom during lectures </p>
            <p id="plaintext">11. Talking in the   library in a loud voice </p>
            <p id="plaintext">12. Using cell phones   in the classroom, lab &amp; the library </p>
            <p id="plaintext">13. Being absent   during the College functions (College Days &amp; Sports Day) </p>
            <p id="plaintext">14. Staining the   campus premises </p>
            <p id="plaintext">15. Misbehaving in   the bus, class and campus in general </p>
